ePlusFan.powerCalculation.c1 + ePlusFan.powerCalculation.c2 * ePlusFan.powerCalculation.f_flow + ePlusFan.powerCalculation.c3 * ePlusFan.powerCalculation.f_flow ^ 2.0 + ePlusFan.powerCalculation.c4 * ePlusFan.powerCalculation.f_flow ^ 3.0

smooth(1, if noEvent(abs(inlet.m_flow) + (-2.0) * ePlusFan.powerCalculation.m_flow_small > ePlusFan.powerCalculation.m_flow_small) then ePlusFan.powerCalculation.f_pl * ePlusFan.powerCalculation.nominalPowerRate else if noEvent(abs(inlet.m_flow) + (-2.0) * ePlusFan.powerCalculation.m_flow_small < (-ePlusFan.powerCalculation.m_flow_small)) then 0.0 else if noEvent(ePlusFan.powerCalculation.m_flow_small > 0.0) then 0.25 * (2.0 - abs(inlet.m_flow) / ePlusFan.powerCalculation.m_flow_small) * ((abs(inlet.m_flow) / ePlusFan.powerCalculation.m_flow_small + -2.0) ^ 2.0 - 3.0) * ePlusFan.powerCalculation.f_pl * ePlusFan.powerCalculation.nominalPowerRate + 0.5 * ePlusFan.powerCalculation.f_pl * ePlusFan.powerCalculation.nominalPowerRate else 0.5 * ePlusFan.powerCalculation.f_pl * ePlusFan.powerCalculation.nominalPowerRate)
